<title>rán shāo ba fú yīn de huǒ 迦南201</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rán shāo ba, rán shāo ba, shèng líng de huǒ rán shāo ba, rán shāo ba, fú yīn de huǒ,
 rán shāo ba, rán shāo zhe zhěng gè zhōng guó, rán shāo ba rán shāo zhe nǐ hé wǒ,
 lā qǐ shǒu chàng qǐ gē, fú yīn yào chéng wèi shì jì de huǒ,
 lā qǐ shǒu chàng qǐ gē, fú yīn yào chéng wèi shì jì de huǒ.</lyrics>
